description:
Imagine the most beautiful thing that you can, the most beautiful thought that you have, and play this polka "Alone At Last!" By Carl Michael Ziehrer, to go along with it, and this piece will compliment the thought that you have, in such a lovely way! 

All of the content in this video belong to its rightful owner, not me. Music from "C.M. Ziehrer: Selected Dances and Marches, Vol. 2" Played by the Razumovsky Symphony Orchestra, conducted by Michael Dittrich.
